Go语言中只有一种for循环语句，但是for语句的语法却最为复杂。for语句的语法规范如下： ForStmt = "for" [ Condition | ForClause | RangeClause ] Block . Condition = Expression . ForClause = [ InitStmt ] ";" [ Condition ] ";" [ PostStmt ] .
InitStmt = SimpleStmt .
PostStmt = SimpleStmt . RangeClause = [ ExpressionList "=" | IdentifierList ":=" ] "range" Expression . 分析语法规范，可以对应以下四种类型： for {}
